      "text": "I had a fireside chat with Former Rep. Rodney Davis &amp; @USChamber Committee of 100 at The Broadmoor about what I'm hearing from Coloradans and my work in Congress on the policies needed to keep our economy growing. https://t.co/d6NiLUtRf5",
