      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/jeff-crank",
      "text": "Today we celebrate America's 250th birthday AND one year since the Working Families Tax Cuts was signed into law!\n\n✅ More money in your pocket\n✅ Bigger Tax Refunds\n✅ Permanent tax relief for small businesses\n✅ Tax break for overtime/tipped workers\n \n@HouseGOP are working https://t.co/ekHJbEVvy3",
