      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/jeff-crank",
      "text": "Today marks a significant chapter in our nation’s story as we celebrate 250 years of American independence and the extraordinary idea that ordinary people could govern themselves.\n\nThis Independence Day, let us reflect on how far we’ve come and celebrate the freedoms we enjoy. https://t.co/YDsDJnxCZD",
