      "ownerName": "Jeff Crank",
      "ownerType": "Congress",
      "countryId": "usa",
      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/jeff-crank",
      "text": "Pleased to hear that Fort Carson has stepped up to help and has already sent multiple crews to assist with the Aspen Acres fire. \n\nThank you to everyone on the frontlines fighting this horrific fire.",
      "createdAt": "2026-07-02T23:21:11Z",
